lead_paragraph: The government’s move to expropriate the building in Braunau am Inn, where Hitler was born in 1889, is intended to remove a site that has drawn neo-Nazis and tourists alike.

headline.print_headline: Austria Seeks to Seize Site Where Hitler Was Born
headline.main: Austria Seeks to Seize, and Possibly Tear Down, Hitler’s House

snippet: The government’s move to expropriate the building in Braunau am Inn, where Hitler was born in 1889, is intended to remove a site that has drawn neo-Nazis and tourists alike....
abstract: Austrian government moves to expropriate building in Braunau am Inn where Adolf Hitler was born; may tear down structure in order to prevent neo-Nazis and tourists from gathering there.
